<H3> <TI>   Mangope in Contact With de Klerk, Mandela </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB1103124594 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 1100 GMT 11 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB1103124594 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The South African and Bophuthatswana presidents were 
in brief telephonic contact this morning, and the minister of 
state affairs of Bophuthatswana, Mr. Rowan Cronje, held talks at 
the Union Buildings for talks with President F.W. de Klerk. 
[sentence as heard] It was not known whether President Lucas 
