<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Franco-Beninese military maneuvers ended in 
Lokossa yesterday with a decoration ceremony and a military 
parade. In view of the results of the five-day maneuvers, our 
