<H3> <TI>   Deadline for Registering Candidate Lists Extended </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB1503095494 Johannesburg SAPA in English 0945 GMT 15 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> MB1503095494 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg SAPA </F>


