Angola [UNITA] Political Commission met in the city of Huambo 
from 12 to 15 March to discuss and clarify the current stage of 
the ongoing Lusaka peace talks; 
  2. The UNITA Political Commission expressed satisfaction 
about UN Special Representative Dr. Alioune Blondin Beye's visit 
