<DOCNO> FBIS3-941 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drafr051_c_94020" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-AFR-94-051 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  15 Mar 1994 </DATE1>

